isabled:pointer-events-none disabled:opacity-50 [&amp;_svg]:pointer-events-none [&amp;_svg:not([class*=&#x27;size-&#x27;])]:size-4 shrink-0 [&amp;_svg]:shrink-0 outline-none focus-visible:border-ring focus-visible:ring-ring/50 focus-visible:ring-[3px] aria-invalid:ring-destructive/20 dark:aria-invalid:ring-destructive/40 aria-invalid:border-destructive bg-primary text-primary-foreground shadow-xs hover:bg-primary/90 h-9 px-4 py-2 has-[&gt;svg]:px-3\">Notify Me</button></div></div></div></div><div class=\"container mx-auto max-w-4xl px-4 py-12\"><h2 class=\"text-2xl font-bold text-center mb-8\">What to Expect</h2><div class=\"grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-4\"><div data-slot=\"card\" class=\"bg-card text-card-foreground flex flex-col gap-6 rounded-xl border py-6 shadow-sm border-emerald-100 hover:border-emerald-300 transition-colors\"><div data-slot=\"card-content\" class=\"p-5\"><div class=\"h-10 w-10 rounded-lg bg-teal-100 flex items-center justify-center mb-3\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-clock h-5 w-5 text-teal-600\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M12 6v6l4 2\"></path><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"10\"></circle></svg></div><h3 class=\"font-semibold mb-2\">Custom Away Messages</h3><p class=\"text-sm text-muted-foreground\">Set personalized away messages that auto-respond when you&#x27;re unavailable. Let clients know when you&#x27;ll be back and provide alternative contact options if needed.</p></div></div><div data-slot=\"card\" class=\"bg-card text-card-foreground flex flex-col gap-6 rounded-xl border py-6 shadow-sm border-emerald-100 hover:border-emerald-300 transition-colors\"><div data-slot=\"card-content\" class=\"p-5\"><div class=\"h-10 w-10 rounded-lg bg-teal-100 flex items-center justify-center mb-3\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-file-text h-5 w-5 text-teal-600\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M15 2H6a2 2 0 0 0-2 2v16a2 2 0 0 0 2 2h12a2 2 0 0 0 2-2V7Z\"></path><path d=\"M14 2v4a2 2 0 0 0 2 2h4\"></path><path d=\"M10 9H8\"></path><path d=\"M16 13H8\"></path><path d=\"M16 17H8\"></path></svg></div><h3 class=\"font-semibold mb-2\">Quick Reply Templates</h3><p class=\"text-sm text-muted-foreground\">Create reusable message templates for common inquiries. Save time by selecting pre-written responses for frequently asked questions about pricing, availability, and services.</p></div></div><div data-slot=\"card\" class=\"bg-card text-card-foreground flex flex-col gap-6 rounded-xl border py-6 shadow-sm border-emerald-100 hover:border-emerald-300 transition-colors\"><div data-slot=\"card-content\" class=\"p-5\"><div class=\"h-10 w-10 rounded-lg bg-teal-100 flex items-center justify-center mb-3\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-sparkles h-5 w-5 text-teal-600\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M9.937 15.5A2 2 0 0 0 8.5 14.063l-6.135-1.582a.5.5 0 0 1 0-.962L8.5 9.936A2 2 0 0 0 9.937 8.5l1.582-6.135a.5.5 0 0 1 .963 0L14.063 8.5A2 2 0 0 0 15.5 9.937l6.135 1.581a.5.5 0 0 1 0 .964L15.5 14.063a2 2 0 0 0-1.437 1.437l-1.582 6.135a.5.5 0 0 1-.963 0z\"></path><path d=\"M20 3v4\"></path><path d=\"M22 5h-4\"></path><path d=\"M4 17v2\"></path><path d=\"M5 18H3\"></path></svg></div><h3 class=\"font-semibold mb-2\">Smart Response Suggestions</h3><p class=\"text-sm text-muted-foreground\">Get AI-powered response suggestions based on the conversation context. Maintain a professional tone while saving time on composing replies to new clients.</p></div></div><div data-slot=\"card\" class=\"bg-card text-card-foreground flex flex-col gap-6 rounded-xl border py-6 shadow-sm border-emerald-100 hover:border-emerald-300 transition-colors\"><div data-slot=\"card-content\" class=\"p-5\"><div class=\"h-10 w-10 rounded-lg bg-teal-100 flex items-center justify-center mb-3\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-message-circle h-5 w-5 text-teal-600\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M7.9 20A9 9 0 1 0 4 16.1L2 22Z\"></path></svg></div><h3 class=\"font-semibold mb-2\">Schedule-Based Auto-Replies</h3><p class=\"text-sm text-muted-foreground\">Configure auto-replies based on your working hours and availability. Automatically respond differently during business hours, evenings, weekends, and holidays.</p></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bg-muted/30 py-12 px-4\"><div class=\"container mx-auto max-w-4xl\"><h2 class=\"text-2xl font-bold text-center mb-8\">How It Will Work</h2><div class=\"grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-4\"><div data-slot=\"card\" class=\"bg-card text-card-foreground flex flex-col gap-6 rounded-xl border py-6 shadow-sm text-center relative\"><div data-slot=\"card-content\" class=\"p-5\"><div class=\"h-10 w-10 rounded-full bg-emerald-600 text-white flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-3 text-sm font-bold\">1</div><h3 class=\"font-semibold mb-2\">Set Your Preferences</h3><p class=\"text-sm text-muted-foreground\">Configure your auto-reply settings including working hours, away status, and default messages. Create a library of quick reply templates for different scenarios.</p><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-arrow-right hidden md:block absolute right-0 top-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 translate-x-1/2 h-5 w-5 text-emerald-300\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M5 12h14\"></path><path d=\"m12 5 7 7-7 7\"></path></svg></div></div><div data-slot=\"card\" class=\"bg-card text-card-foreground flex flex-col gap-6 rounded-xl border py-6 shadow-sm text-center relative\"><div data-slot=\"card-content\" class=\"p-5\"><div class=\"h-10 w-10 rounded-full bg-emerald-600 text-white flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-3 text-sm font-bold\">2</div><h3 class=\"font-semibold mb-2\">Enable Auto-Reply</h3><p class=\"text-sm text-muted-foreground\">Turn on auto-reply for specific situations — when you&#x27;re busy, away, or outside working hours. Choose which conversations should receive automated responses.</p><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-arrow-right hidden md:block absolute right-0 top-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 translate-x-1/2 h-5 w-5 text-emerald-300\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M5 12h14\"></path><path d=\"m12 5 7 7-7 7\"></path></svg></div></div><div data-slot=\"card\" class=\"bg-card text-card-foreground flex flex-col gap-6 rounded-xl border py-6 shadow-sm text-center relative\"><div data-slot=\"card-content\" class=\"p-5\"><div class=\"h-10 w-10 rounded-full bg-emerald-600 text-white flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-3 text-sm font-bold\">3</div><h3 class=\"font-semibold mb-2\">Review &amp; Customize</h3><p class=\"text-sm text-muted-foreground\">Monitor your auto-reply activity and see which templates are most used. Fine-tune your messages based on client feedback and improve response quality over time.</p></div></div></div></div></div><div class=\"container mx-auto max-w-4xl px-4 py-12 text-center\"><p class=\"text-muted-foreground mb-4\">In the meantime, explore related tools:</p><div class=\"flex flex-wrap gap-2 justify-center\"><a href=\"/dashboa